# Project Rules

## Component & File Naming
- Use kebab-case for file/folder names, not PascalCase
- Example: `user-profile` instead of `UserProfile`

## Code Style
- All comments must be in English, regardless of the language used in user questions
- Use `lucide-react` for icons

## Internationalization (i18n)
- Use react-i18next as the i18n solution
- Language files location:
  - /locales/en.json (English)
  - /locales/zh.json (Chinese)
- Use flat mode for i18n keys:
  - Keys should be separated by dots
  - Avoid nested JSON objects
  - ✅ Good: `"common.badge.alpha": "Alpha"`
  - ❌ Bad: 
    ```json
    {
      "common": {
        "badge": {
          "alpha": "Alpha"
        }
      }
    }
    ```